rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, thanks for coming! As you can
see, we made it to Superbia in one
piece!

rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0002
rows.name:
I feel bad about doing that to
Rhiannon's parents, I really do...

rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0003
rows.name:
But Rhiannon's happiness is what's
most important to me.

rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, before I forget, there's something
I've been meaning to give you. Here.

rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0101
rows.name:
It looks like I might have made things
more difficult than I thought for
Rhiannon, moving to Superbia.

rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0102
rows.name:
There's all the tension with Invidia
and the Divine Beast getting weaker... It's
one thing after the other, really.

rows.label: tlk4130009101_msg0103
rows.name:
But I'll do everything I can to support
her! I promised her a better life and
that's what she'll have, you'll see!
